<% provide(:title, 'Home') %>

<div class="titletext">
<h1>80% of success in life is showing up. - Woody Allen</h1>
<br><br>
<p class="lead">Groupify lets you sign up for nearby group events and rewards you for staying committed.</p>
 <%= button_to "Sign Up", signup_path, :class => "btn btn-success btn-large", :method => 'get'%>
</div>
<hr>

<p class="lead"> Groups Forming Now</p>
<% @group.take(5).each do |g| %>
<div class="panel panel-info">
  <div class="panel-heading"><%= g.title %></div>
    <div class="panel-footer">
      People Going: 
      <span class="badge"><%= g.attendances.count %></span>
    </div>
  </div>
 <% end %>


<hr>
<h1>Groupify Karma</h1>

<p class="lead">
<ol>
  <li>Everytime you sign up for a deal, you earn karma.</li>
  <li><s>Everyone hates flakes.</s> Others lose more than just money when you cancel.</li>
  <li>When you don't show up, you lose. In fact, everyone loses. Not making good on your promises has negative consequences in our system.</li>
  <li>Have feedback? Let us know by emailing us at groupmaster@usegroupify.com. </li>
</ol>
</p>
<hr>
</div>


